66 fund, the division of tourism shall present to the special committee on tourism[, recreational
67 and cultural affairs] of the house of representatives and to the [transportation and tourism]
68 economic and workforce development committee of the senate, or their successors, a
69 promotional marketing strategy including, but not limited to, targeted markets, duration of
